### ============================================
### Create Payment - Below Minimum (Should Fail)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: manual-test-003

{
  "amount": 25,
  "currency": "usd",
  "description": "This should fail - below 50 cents"
}

